_readme: • Set "include": false to remove a river from terrain processing
• Add notes in the "notes" field to document your reasoning
• Entries marked confidence: "review" need manual verification
"review"   — scalerank 6-7, may be <60m — verify before shipping
"measured" — OSM has actual width data confirming ≥60m
WIDTH CLASSES (estimated from scalerank, not measured):
The terrain processor uses this file to decide which OSM waterways
to check for hex-edge crossings at the 10km strategic scale.
Rivers not in this list are ignored during strategic map generation.
